 rustup target add x86_64-pc-windows-gnu                                                                            
  sudo apt install gcc-mingw-w64-x86-64  
  cargo run --package xtask --release -- bundle rt-autotune --release --target x86_64-pc-windows-gnu                 
                                                                                                    
  Then copy target/bundled/rt-autotune.vst3 to your FL Studio VST3 folder (typically C:\Program Files\Common         
  Files\VST3\).                                                                  